  "text": "With the system is in open-loop mode, Step the process input by a small amount (\u2206u) and record the output response till it reaches new steady state as shown in Figure (11) . From the obtained response for the output determine the process parameters, gain process(K p ), open loop time constant (\u03c4) and dead time(\u03b8) [CITATION_1] .",
